    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>I don&#39;t know if you guys have it over there, but borage (starflower) is THE traditional thing to put in Pimm&#39;s (and so pretty too). Cucumber is easier to get hold of, but borage is the classic. The flowers are edible as well, and taste faintly cucumber-y.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.westcountryorganicherbs.co.uk/borage.JPG" rel="nofollow ugc">http://www.westcountryorganicherbs.co.uk/borage.JPG</a></p>
