    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>had Pimm&#39;s #1 Cup at Wimbledon 3 weeks ago (my 1st trip to Europe, my 1st Pimm&#39;s!)It was so hot and it tasted so good!  You nailed it, refreshing.  The cucumber, mint, orange and lemon all seemed necessary.  Did the limonata work?  or Vernor&#39;s? I&#39;d best get busy&#8230;currently 93 here in the midwest, so we need this!</p>
