    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>As a UK girl, I have tried many variations on Pimms; my favourite is a version we call Classic Pimms, which involves 1 x bottle of Pimms, 1/2 bottle Cointreau, 1/3 bottle brandy, 1 x bottle of lemonade and 2 x bottle tonic, split evenly into pitchers, muddled with mountains of mint and topped with wafer thin cucumber slices &#8211; absolute heaven for a big party punch!</p>
